        How to Stage a Small Brisbane Home or Unit for Sale on a Tight Budget
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Small properties need more preparation than larger ones, not less. Here is how to present a compact apartment or townhouse in Brisbane's inner east so buyers see the space clearly and price it accordingly.
      </p>
